section_title: Compilation and synthesis of supplementary information in fifth national communications of Annex I parties that are also parties to the Kyoto Protocol
sentences: This agenda sub-item (FCCC/SBI/2011/INF.2) was first addressed in the SBI plenary on 10 June.
It was considered in a contact group and informal consultations co-chaired by Helen Plume and Diann Black Layne.
During the closing plenary on 16 June, the SBI agreed to continue consideration of the issue at SBI 35.
